      <title>Hexo NexT</title>
      <link href="/blog/post/429b577f.html"/>
      <url>/blog/post/429b577f.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo 是高效的静态站点生成框架，她基于 Node.js。 通过 Hexo 你可以轻松地使用 Markdown 编写文章，除了 Markdown 本身的语法之外，还可以使用 Hexo 提供的 标签插件 来快速的插入特定形式的内容。在这篇文章中，假定你已经成功安装了 Hexo，并使用 Hexo 提供的命令创建了一个站点。</p><p>Hexo原项目已经停止维护，NexTv6和v7版本有社区维护[<a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next]" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next]</a></p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="一、安装NexT"><a href="#一、安装NexT" class="headerlink" title="一、安装NexT"></a>一、安装NexT</h2><h2 id="1、进入Hexo目录"><a href="#1、进入Hexo目录" class="headerlink" title="1、进入Hexo目录"></a>1、进入Hexo目录</h2><p>进入 Hexo 根目录。这一目录中应当有 node_modules、source、themes 等若干子目录：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ cd hexo</span><br><span class="line">$ ls</span><br><span class="line">_config.yml  node_modules  package.json  public  scaffolds  source  themes</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2、获取-NexT"><a href="#2、获取-NexT" class="headerlink" title="2、获取 NexT"></a>2、获取 NexT</h2><p>使用 git 安装</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;theme-next&#x2F;hexo-theme-next themes&#x2F;next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这一方式将为你下载完整仓库（其中包含 .git 目录）。<br>你可以随时使用 git 更新至最新版本并切换至任何有 tag 标记的 release 版本、最新的 master 分支版本、甚至其他分支。<br>在绝大多数情况下对用户和开发者友好。</p><p>获取 tags 列表：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ cd themes&#x2F;next</span><br><span class="line">$ git tag -l</span><br><span class="line">…</span><br><span class="line">v6.0.0</span><br><span class="line">v6.0.1</span><br><span class="line">v6.0.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>例如，假设你想要切换到 v7.8.0 这一 tag 指向的 release 版本。输入如下指令：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git checkout tags&#x2F;v7.8.0</span><br><span class="line">Note: checking out &#39;tags&#x2F;v7.8.0&#39;.</span><br><span class="line">…</span><br><span class="line">HEAD is now at f995680 Release v7.8.0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3、完成配置"><a href="#3、完成配置" class="headerlink" title="3、完成配置"></a>3、完成配置</h2><p>在 Hexo 站点配置文件（/_config.yml）中设置你的主题：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4、验证配置"><a href="#4、验证配置" class="headerlink" title="4、验证配置"></a>4、验证配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 当命令行输出中提示出：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  Hexo is running at http:&#x2F;&#x2F;localhost:4000 . Press Ctrl+C to stop.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此时即可使用浏览器访问 <a href="http://localhost:4000，检查站点是否正确运行。">http://localhost:4000，检查站点是否正确运行。</a></p><h2 id="二、Hexo配置"><a href="#二、Hexo配置" class="headerlink" title="二、Hexo配置"></a>二、Hexo配置</h2><p>Hexo配置部分参考 <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/</a></p><h2 id="1、配置Site信息"><a href="#1、配置Site信息" class="headerlink" title="1、配置Site信息"></a>1、配置Site信息</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: Luhy&#39;s BLOG</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: &#39;&#39;</span><br><span class="line">description: 天道酬勤</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">author: Luhy</span><br><span class="line">language: zh-CN  &#x2F;&#x2F;此处需根据themes对应语言包设置</span><br><span class="line">timezone: Asia&#x2F;Shanghai</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2、配置URL信息"><a href="#2、配置URL信息" class="headerlink" title="2、配置URL信息"></a>2、配置URL信息</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;xxx.gitee.io&#x2F;blog </span><br><span class="line">root: &#x2F;blog</span><br><span class="line">permalink: :year&#x2F;:month&#x2F;:day&#x2F;:title&#x2F;</span><br><span class="line">permalink_defaults:</span><br><span class="line">pretty_urls:</span><br><span class="line">  trailing_index: true</span><br><span class="line">  trailing_html: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3、配置Deployment信息"><a href="#3、配置Deployment信息" class="headerlink" title="3、配置Deployment信息"></a>3、配置Deployment信息</h2><p>配置部署信息，将部署文件部署到gitee或github</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https:&#x2F;&#x2F;gitee.com&#x2F;xxx&#x2F;blog.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><strong>如果hexo d部署报错ERROR Deployer not found: git ，则需要安装组件</strong></p></blockquote><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4、配置博客文章持久化连接"><a href="#4、配置博客文章持久化连接" class="headerlink" title="4、配置博客文章持久化连接"></a>4、配置博客文章持久化连接</h2><p><strong>安装hexo-abbrlink这个插件</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-abbrlink --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>_config.yml文件修改permalink添加如下内容</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">permalink: post&#x2F;:abbrlink.html</span><br><span class="line">abbrlink:</span><br><span class="line">  alg: crc32  </span><br><span class="line">  rep: hex   </span><br><span class="line">permalink_defaults:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="三、NexT主题配置"><a href="#三、NexT主题配置" class="headerlink" title="三、NexT主题配置"></a>三、NexT主题配置</h2><h2 id="1、主题样式配置"><a href="#1、主题样式配置" class="headerlink" title="1、主题样式配置"></a>1、主题样式配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Schemes</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Muse</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Mist</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Pisces</span><br><span class="line">scheme: Gemini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2、菜单配置"><a href="#2、菜单配置" class="headerlink" title="2、菜单配置"></a>2、菜单配置</h2><p>将about、tags、categories前的#号去掉,示例如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: &#x2F; || home</span><br><span class="line">  about: &#x2F;about&#x2F; || user</span><br><span class="line">  tags: &#x2F;tags&#x2F; || tags</span><br><span class="line">  categories: &#x2F;categories&#x2F; || th</span><br><span class="line">  archives: &#x2F;archives&#x2F; || archive</span><br><span class="line">  #schedule: &#x2F;schedule&#x2F; || calendar</span><br><span class="line">  #sitemap: &#x2F;sitemap.xml || sitemap</span><br><span class="line">  #commonweal: &#x2F;404&#x2F; || heartbeat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>新建页面</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;about&quot;</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page &quot;categories&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>修改新增页面</strong></p><ul><li>source\about\index.md</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 关于</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;about&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>source\tags\index.md</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 标签</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>source\categories\index.md</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 分类</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3、添加搜索功能"><a href="#3、添加搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="3、添加搜索功能"></a>3、添加搜索功能</h2><p><strong>安装exo-generator-searchdb这个插件</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>修改_config.yml添加搜索配置</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">search:</span><br><span class="line">  path: search.xml</span><br><span class="line">  field: post</span><br><span class="line">  format: html</span><br><span class="line">  limit: 10000</span><br><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4、设置头像"><a href="#4、设置头像" class="headerlink" title="4、设置头像"></a>4、设置头像</h2><p><strong>将头像放置主题目录下的 source/images/ 目录下</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">avatar:</span><br><span class="line">  url: &#x2F;images&#x2F;avatar.gif</span><br><span class="line">  rounded: true</span><br><span class="line">  rotated: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5、集成百度统计"><a href="#5、集成百度统计" class="headerlink" title="5、集成百度统计"></a>5、集成百度统计</h2><p><strong>登录百度统计 <a href="https://tongji.baidu.com/web/welcome/login" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://tongji.baidu.com/web/welcome/login</a></strong></p><p><strong>添加统计网站，获取相关程序</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">var _hmt &#x3D; _hmt || [];</span><br><span class="line">(function() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  var hm &#x3D; document.createElement(&quot;script&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">  hm.src &#x3D; &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hm.baidu.com&#x2F;hm.js?baidu_analytics&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">  var s &#x3D; document.getElementsByTagName(&quot;script&quot;)[0]; </span><br><span class="line">  s.parentNode.insertBefore(hm, s);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)();</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>编辑主题配置文件， 修改字段 baidu_analytics 字段，值设置成你的百度统计脚本 id。</strong></p><h2 id="6、添加站点运行时间"><a href="#6、添加站点运行时间" class="headerlink" title="6、添加站点运行时间"></a>6、添加站点运行时间</h2><p><strong>在themes\next\layout_partials\footer.swig中添加如下代码：</strong> </p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;timeDate&quot;&gt;载入天数...&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;span id&#x3D;&quot;times&quot;&gt;载入时分秒...&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      var now &#x3D; new Date();</span><br><span class="line">      function createtime() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          var grt&#x3D; new Date(&quot;07&#x2F;28&#x2F;2020 00:00:00&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">          now.setTime(now.getTime()+250);</span><br><span class="line">          days &#x3D; (now - grt ) &#x2F; 1000 &#x2F; 60 &#x2F; 60 &#x2F; 24; dnum &#x3D; Math.floor(days);</span><br><span class="line">          hours &#x3D; (now - grt ) &#x2F; 1000 &#x2F; 60 &#x2F; 60 - (24 * dnum); hnum &#x3D; Math.floor(hours);</span><br><span class="line">          if(String(hnum).length &#x3D;&#x3D;1 )&#123;hnum &#x3D; &quot;0&quot; + hnum;&#125; minutes &#x3D; (now - grt ) &#x2F; 1000 &#x2F;60 - (24 * 60 * dnum) - (60 * hnum);</span><br><span class="line">          mnum &#x3D; Math.floor(minutes); if(String(mnum).length &#x3D;&#x3D;1 )&#123;mnum &#x3D; &quot;0&quot; + mnum;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">          seconds &#x3D; (now - grt ) &#x2F; 1000 - (24 * 60 * 60 * dnum) - (60 * 60 * hnum) - (60 * mnum);</span><br><span class="line">          snum &#x3D; Math.round(seconds); if(String(snum).length &#x3D;&#x3D;1 )&#123;snum &#x3D; &quot;0&quot; + snum;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">          document.getElementById(&quot;timeDate&quot;).innerHTML &#x3D; &quot;本站已运行 &quot;+dnum+&quot; 天 &quot;;</span><br><span class="line">          document.getElementById(&quot;times&quot;).innerHTML &#x3D; hnum + &quot; 小时 &quot; + mnum + &quot; 分 &quot; + snum + &quot; 秒&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br><span class="line">     setInterval(&quot;createtime()&quot;,250);</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
